origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'CryptoMarketAPI.get_liquidity_analysis', 'description': 'This function provides liquidity analysis for a specified cryptocurrency within a given time frame.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'cryptoName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the cryptocurrency to analyze.'}, {'name': 'timeFrame', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time frame for the liquidity analysis, e.g., lastMonth, lastYear.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'liquidityReport', 'description': 'A detailed liquidity analysis report for the specified cryptocurrency.'}]}
请用以下格式进行回复:
想法: 你这一步的目标
动作: 你要调用的API名称
动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 CryptoMarketAPI.get_liquidity_analysis, 它的参数输入如下: 'cryptoName'是'SushiSwap', 'timeFrame'是'lastMonth'.
